      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like i'm stuck in this loop. every time i think about the future i just see nothing. like a big dark hole. it's not even sadness anymore, it's just... exhaustion. i'm so tired of trying to fight it. why am i even trying to make it through the day?",
